xplicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wedevs.com/?p=87404\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:586:\"<p>If you are planning to start your eCommerce business, the first hurdle that you will come across is selecting the website platform. Why? Because this is the pillar of your business. When the pillar is not built wisely, the structure might collapse at any time. This is why you need to pick the right platform [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87404/why-use-woocommerce-for-ecommerce/\">Not Using WooCommerce to Build Your Ecommerce Website? Think Again!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/account\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Rafi Nizamee\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10702:\"<p>If you are planning to start your eCommerce business, the first hurdle that you will come across is selecting the website platform. Why? Because this is the pillar of your business. When the pillar is not built wisely, the structure might collapse at any time. This is why you need to pick the right platform for your eCommerce.</p>\r\n<p>Creating a self-managed online store seems difficult for regular users. But with modern technology, you do not need to be a super techie or have a degree in computer engineering for that. If you can pick the right eCommerce engine for your website, it will do more than half the job for you. Luckily for us, we have <a href=\"https://wphive.com/plugins/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce</a> &#8211; the most customizable and user friendly eCommerce platform for building an online business. It has been downloaded more than 121 million times. Just take a moment to think of the impact this plugin has over the global eCommerce industry!</p>\r\n<p>In this article, we will discuss what makes WooCommerce so special in terms of usability and reach. Why WooCommerce stands out from its powerful competitors like Magento, Shopify, or Etsy.</p>\r\n<h2>1. WooCommerce is FREE!</h2>\r\n<p>Cost is a serious consideration for any business. <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/idea/woocommerce-points-rewards-integration/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce is as good as it can</a> get on this front because it is completely free! The major competitor of WooCommerce is not so generous. For example, you need to buy a pricing plan to get started with Shopify. Besides that, a certain percentage of commission is charged at each checkout.  Etsy can be downloaded for free but it charges $0.20 for each listed product.</p>\r\n<h2>2. You Don\'t Need to Worry About Security</h2>\r\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/12/point2520of2520sale2520system2520for2520woocommerce2520pos2520plugin-1024x559.png\" alt=\"woocommerce shop\" /></p>\r\n<p>Having a protected transaction process is a must for any solid eCommerce website. Also, the website must not be vulnerable to hacking and other external malware. WooCommerce lets you be at the top of your game by releasing frequent updates. This way, you do not have to worry about security issues. Another awesome thing is that WooCommerce is monitored by the best website security platform <a href=\"https://sucuri.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sucuri</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Apart from these, there are plenty of resources all over the internet about how to tackle any kind of problem with WooCommerce. It is <strong>the most trusted eCommerce builder</strong> for a reason!</p>\r\n<h2>3. Customize Your Website As Much As You Want</h2>\r\n<p>WooCommerce might be free, but don\'t think it only provides a basic platform with ZERO customization. The reality is the exact opposite of this assumption. You can select from thousands of themes and plugins if you are using WooCommerce for your eCommerce business. These are being used by numerous online businesses. If you are looking for customizing your website, WooCommerce is the best option for you.</p>\r\n<p>So, why do you need to reinvent the wheel?</p>\r\n<h2>4. WooCommerce Includes Powerful Analytics</h2>\r\n<p>In order to increase the conversion rate, you must know about your customers and the way they interact with your online shop. WooCommerce can help you in that. WooCommerce provides an an extensive set of analytics displayed in a clear and intuitive interface. Moreover, it\'s simple to integrate WooCommerce with any third-party analytics services like Google Analytics with extensions.</p>\r\n<h2>5. Expect Every Possible Functionality</h2>\r\n<p>Ecommerce entrepreneurs typically struggle with product offerings and payment methods. For example, you might want to sell both tangible products like mobile sets and subscription products like violin courses. WooCommerce gives you the easy features to sell literally ANYTHING! Read the following blog to know more about how you can explore product variety to take your eCommerce to the next level.</p>\r\n<p>You may also like to read: <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87025/types-of-products-you-can-create-using-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How You Can Sell Anything with WooCommerce</a></p>\r\n<p>On top of that, WooCommerce supports <a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">more than 140 payment gateways</a> to cater to your needs. It is safe to say no other eCommerce builders have ever come close to this platform in terms of quality and number of payment gateways. No matter where your customers live, they can purchase from your store comfortably and safely.</p>\r\n<h2>6. Guarantees Search Engine Optimization</h2>\r\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2019/10/460.-The-Complete-Guide-to-WooCommerce-SEO-1024x559.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce SEO guide\" /></p>\r\n<p>Ensuring a high ranking on search engines must be one of the topmost priorities for eCommerce owners. According to a study, more than 40% of online shoppers search for a product before making a purchase decision. WooCommerce undoubtedly leads this race since it is powered by WordPress. <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/229616/ultimate-woocommerce-seo-guide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Optimizing website content</a> can not get easier than in WordPress.</p>\r\n<h2>7. WooCommerce Has A Vibrant Developer Community</h2>\r\n<p>WooCommerce is entirely open source, which means you can modify or add core features, build new extensions, and develop custom themes as well. For some other eCommerce applications, it\'s difficult to manage any programmer who are capable working on that or if you find anyone, s/he is expensive to hire.</p>\r\n<p>On the other hand, you can easily find someone who can customize your WooCommerce store. Or you can also do it by yourself by going through some easy tutorials and blog as this eCommerce platform is super easy to perform.</p>\r\n<h2>8. WooCommerce is Made For Selling</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/187759/woocommerce-tutorial-build-an-online-store-within-minutes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce is designed</a> dedicatedly to sell products online. So, an online retrailer will find everything s/he needs to set and run an online shop successfully.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Very easy to use &#8211; download, install and go</li>\r\n<li>Offer Flexible and Secure Payments- 140 region-specific gateways to choose from and integrate with</li>\r\n<li>Simple to update products and fulfill orders through WooCommerce dashboard</li>\r\n<li>Automated tax calculations, live shipping rates from leading carriers, options to print labels at home, and the mobile app for iOS and Android.</li>\r\n<li>A number of customizable and mobile-friendly free & premium WooCommerce themes are available. Or build a custom theme to give your store an elegant look</li>\r\n<li>Helpful documentation that gives the guidance for new eCommerce retailers to operate a shop smoothly.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>In short, WooCommerce is the complete package that is fast, simple to use, and can adapt to the needs of your eCommerce business.</p>\r\n<h2>9. Rich and Exclusive Extension Marketplace</h2>\r\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/The-importance-of-Customer-Support-for-online-marketplaces-1-1024x559.png\" alt=\"importance of customer service\" /></p>\r\n<p>WooCommerce offers over more than 500 official and countless 3rd party extensions to build your marketplace in the best possible way. These extensions cover every possible payment method, data import-export, accounting & marketing modules, product types, reporting & analytics, membership, and so on! These extensions are way ahead of their competitors in terms of both quality and review.</p>\r\n<p>You can check out all the WooCommerce extensions by <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/extensions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">clicking on this link</a>.</p>\r\n<h2>Build Your Own eBay Effortlessly</h2>\r\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2019/08/Installing-WooCommerce-1024x559.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce tutorial\" /></p>\r\n<p>Since you are reading this article, chances are high that you have considered starting your own marketplace like eBay at some point. Let me give you good news. You can now easily <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87354/create-ebay-like-marketplace-using-dokan-multivendor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">create a multi-vendor marketplace with Dokan</a> which is powered by WooCommerce. It adds another solid point in favor of using WooCommerce, right? Sadly, other hosted solutions do not have such awesome features.</p>\r\n<h2>Over to You&#8230;..</h2>\r\n<p>There is no doubt WooCommerce makes creating and managing an online store simple, with a wide range of flexibility and a lot of useful features like inventory and tax management, secure payments and shipping integration. If you\'re looking to run an eCommerce store, WooCommerce could be the best choice. </p>\r\n<p>Also, you can extend its core functionality using different plugins and extensions. It enables you to handle different store models on the same platform. So, if you are still in the dialema- &#8220;Why use WooCommerce for eCommerce&#8221;- It\'s beacause-</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>WooCommerce is free</li>\r\n<li>Provides a simple and intuitive interface</li>\r\n<li>It\'s constantly evolving and improving</li>\r\n<li>You can add any functionality to improve WooCommerce</li>\r\n<li>Easy to use – download, install and go</li>\r\n<li>Hundreds of plugins and integrations available</li>\r\n<li>It\'s popular- a lot of people rely on this platform</li>\r\n<li>You can sell what you want, the way you want!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>It\'s your time to take the final decision. Don\'t forget to share your opinion in the comment section bellow. </p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://wedevs.com/dokan/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" class=\"wp-image-332131\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/10/dokan-dream-multivendor-business-2.gif\" alt=\"dokan multivendor\" /></a></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87404/why-use-woocommerce-for-ecommerce/\">Not Using WooCommerce to Build Your Ecommerce Website? Think Again!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/account\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87404/why-use-woocommerce-for-ecommerce/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"9 Proven Ways to Boost Your eCommerce Sales\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87132/proven-ways-to-boost-ecommerce-sales/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87132/proven-ways-to-boost-ecommerce-sales/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 06 Jun 2020 18:57:43 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Dokan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Tips and Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"ecommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"growth hack\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wedevs.com/?p=87132\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:546:\"<p>Do you have an established eCommerce store? A good customer base? Competitive products and services with a price set better than the rest of the market? And in spite of all, does it seem that your sales have become stagnant over time? If you said yes to all of the above, know that this is [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87132/proven-ways-to-boost-ecommerce-sales/\">9 Proven Ways to Boost Your eCommerce Sales</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/account\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Rounak Ahmed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18624:\"\r\n<p>Do you have an established eCommerce store? A good customer base? Competitive products and services with a price set better than the rest of the market? And in spite of all, does it seem that your sales have become stagnant over time?</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If you said yes to all of the above, know that this is not a dead-end. You can boost your company\'s growth and sales again with some well-known methods. The only thing is you have to be persistent with these efforts in your business.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>We are going to show you some proven and useful strategy you can follow to rejuvenate your eCommerce store into a new life.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><span id=\"more-87132\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Try Out These 9 Steps To Revamp Your Sales & Boost Your Revenue!</h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"811\" height=\"443\" class=\"wp-image-90693\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2016/10/How-Coupons-and-Discounts-Rapidly-Boost-Your-Store-Sales.png\" alt=\"boost sales using coupons\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2016/10/How-Coupons-and-Discounts-Rapidly-Boost-Your-Store-Sales.png 811w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2016/10/How-Coupons-and-Discounts-Rapidly-Boost-Your-Store-Sales-300x164.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2016/10/How-Coupons-and-Discounts-Rapidly-Boost-Your-Store-Sales-768x420.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2016/10/How-Coupons-and-Discounts-Rapidly-Boost-Your-Store-Sales-600x328.png 600w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2016/10/How-Coupons-and-Discounts-Rapidly-Boost-Your-Store-Sales-750x410.png 750w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2016/10/How-Coupons-and-Discounts-Rapidly-Boost-Your-Store-Sales-810x443.png 810w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 811px) 100vw, 811px\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Below we bring to you some golden tips, though well known yet sometimes underrated, that brought our business and those of our peers in the industry a steady growth in terms of sales.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Utilize Offline Connections</li>\r\n<li>Leverage Social Media Platforms</li>\r\n<li>Offer More Coupons, Discounts and Contests</li>\r\n<li>Become A Regular Blog Writer</li>\r\n<li>Sponsor Appropriate Events and Fairs</li>\r\n<li>Keep Growing Your Email List</li>\r\n<li>Make Use of Online Ads</li>\r\n<li>Grow Better With Mobile Optimization</li>\r\n<li>Paid Traffic</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>01. <strong>Utilize Offline Connections</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>To do this bring online your connections that you made through personal networking. These include your family, friends, and any connections you have made through acquaintances and people who you have met in events and different occasions.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Bring those influential people, businessmen, and individuals whom you have come to know through mutual friends and relatives. Take their emails, add them up on Facebook, follow on Twitter, Pinterest, Instagram, wherever you may find them, and leave no scope to let them know of your online business!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>02. <strong>Leverage Social Media Platforms</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Social media today is <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/78123/social-engagement-important-business/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">one of the better and effective ways today to reach your customers.</a> Install plugins for your social profiles on your website and eCommerce platform so users can directly follow and like your page without the hassle of going to a different window. Post daily updates and know your customers and their needs by interacting with them regularly.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"wp-image-102477\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2017/11/social-media-marketing-services-clock.gif\" alt=\"social media\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>With several online solutions available for amateurs to create images and videos for their business, it has now become even more handy for you to reach out better to your customers through social media. Not always you have to hire designers, sometimes you can throw in some creatives made by you!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>03. <strong>Offer More Coupons, Discounts and Contests</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"559\" class=\"wp-image-263833\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/Digital-Coupons-What-why-when-how-to-create-them_-1024x559.png\" alt=\"Digital Coupons What, why, when & how to create them_\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/Digital-Coupons-What-why-when-how-to-create-them_-1024x559.png 1024w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/Digital-Coupons-What-why-when-how-to-create-them_-300x164.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/Digital-Coupons-What-why-when-how-to-create-them_-768x420.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/Digital-Coupons-What-why-when-how-to-create-them_-1536x839.png 1536w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/Digital-Coupons-What-why-when-how-to-create-them_-45x25.png 45w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/Digital-Coupons-What-why-when-how-to-create-them_-112x61.png 112w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/Digital-Coupons-What-why-when-how-to-create-them_.png 1622w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/80662/boost-sales-using-coupon-discount/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">importance of offering giveaway contests, bonuses, coupons, and special offers</a> to your regular customers cannot be underestimated. But it not only helps to make your regular clients more loyal to you, but it also increases your leads and makes your offerings more attractive to potential clients.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>04. <strong>Become A Regular Blog Writer</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"559\" class=\"wp-image-156191\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2019/01/How-to-get-more-comments-on-blogs-updated-1024x559.png\" alt=\"Get more comments blogs posts\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2019/01/How-to-get-more-comments-on-blogs-updated-1024x559.png 1024w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2019/01/How-to-get-more-comments-on-blogs-updated-300x164.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2019/01/How-to-get-more-comments-on-blogs-updated-768x420.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2019/01/How-to-get-more-comments-on-blogs-updated-750x410.png 750w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2019/01/How-to-get-more-comments-on-blogs-updated.png 1622w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Keep your customers up to date and informed about your business with regular blogs. Your <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/302626/blogging-with-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">blogs</a> should feature not only updates about your service or product but also how you are willing to help your clients grow through your offerings, how you vision your business, and how you are making an impact in the lives of your customers.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>05. <strong>Sponsor Appropriate Events and Fairs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If budget allows, participate in different local fairs and conferences that are relevant to your business and fields. Also consider sponsoring products and services in these fairs and conferences that will represent your seriousness and passion about the services and products you sell.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>06. <strong>Keep Growing Your Email List</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"547\" class=\"wp-image-263170\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/WordPress-Email-Marketing-Tools-Compared-1024x547.png\" alt=\"WordPress Email Marketing Plugins\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/WordPress-Email-Marketing-Tools-Compared-1024x547.png 1024w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/WordPress-Email-Marketing-Tools-Compared-300x160.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/WordPress-Email-Marketing-Tools-Compared-768x410.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/WordPress-Email-Marketing-Tools-Compared-1536x820.png 1536w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/WordPress-Email-Marketing-Tools-Compared-45x24.png 45w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/WordPress-Email-Marketing-Tools-Compared-112x60.png 112w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/WordPress-Email-Marketing-Tools-Compared.png 1540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Use referral programs to <a href=\"https://getwemail.io/email-marketing-best-practices-to-boost-your-sales/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">create email lists that will increase your leads</a> whom you can send subscription requests. Create subscription pop-ups in your blogs and eCommerce site. Send welcome emails, and follow up emails to new customers after a purchase. You can also send newsletters on weekly blogs. Make as much free offerings as possible.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>07. <strong>Make Use of Online Ads</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"559\" class=\"wp-image-294978\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Retargeting-Ads-Best-Practices-2-1024x559.png\" alt=\"Retargeting Ads Best Practices\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Retargeting-Ads-Best-Practices-2-1024x559.png 1024w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Retargeting-Ads-Best-Practices-2-300x164.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Retargeting-Ads-Best-Practices-2-768x420.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Retargeting-Ads-Best-Practices-2-1536x839.png 1536w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Retargeting-Ads-Best-Practices-2-45x25.png 45w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Retargeting-Ads-Best-Practices-2-112x61.png 112w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Retargeting-Ads-Best-Practices-2.png 1622w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Use Google, Gmail and Facebook ads to reach your target customers. All of these sources have amazing targeting and customization features and are very popular among all types of businesses. With Google Ads, you are able to track both clicks and conversions to your ads. It is very powerful given that it is the most popular search engine and you can play around with keywords to <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/292617/retargeting-ads-best-practices/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">create ad campaigns</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Create campaigns on Facebook and target them to the right group of audience by sponsoring. Now with Facebook video ads, which work similar to YouTube ads, you can showcase the creativity of your business. Also use Gmail ads to target the same keywords as your competitors so buyers who are purchasing from them will also see your ads in their inboxes.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>08. <strong>Grow Better With Mobile Optimization</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>With the huge impact of smartphones in everyone’s lives and the growth in smartphone users, it has become ever more essential to <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/286262/top-features-for-online-marketplace-platform/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">make your website and overall business mobile-friendly. </a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"811\" height=\"443\" class=\"wp-image-267679\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/mobile-ecommerce.png\" alt=\"mobile ecommerce\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/mobile-ecommerce.png 811w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/mobile-ecommerce-300x164.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/mobile-ecommerce-768x420.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/mobile-ecommerce-45x25.png 45w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/01/mobile-ecommerce-112x61.png 112w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 811px) 100vw, 811px\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>A large number of smartphone users are heavily influenced by online ads and products displayed attractively. So it is essential to make your online site mobile friendly. Though more often than not you have to get a professional solution to make your site mobile friendly, the investment does pay off. You will realize this when you see growth in your sales again.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>09. Paid Traffic</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>One might think <a href=\"https://wphive.com/tutorials/google-paid-search-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">paid traffic</a> is expensive nowadays. However, it can generate sales for your eCommerce store.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>But if done properly paid traffic can, in fact, be quite affordable and once you have a winning campaign on your hands, paid traffic can really take your business to the next level.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"559\" class=\"wp-image-288083\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Total-Traffic-in-2019-1024x559.png\" alt=\"Total Traffic in 2019\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Total-Traffic-in-2019-1024x559.png 1024w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Total-Traffic-in-2019-300x164.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Total-Traffic-in-2019-768x420.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Total-Traffic-in-2019-1536x839.png 1536w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Total-Traffic-in-2019-45x25.png 45w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Total-Traffic-in-2019-112x61.png 112w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/03/Total-Traffic-in-2019.png 1622w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>You need to start with small amounts to &#8220;test the water&#8221; before actually starting. There is common myth that dumping a lot of money for paid traffic can bring good results. Well, that is totally wrong.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Spending a small amount on these platforms can teach you a lot.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/76567/tips-for-market-owners/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Marketing Tips For New Market Owners</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Here is the short visualization that you might like. Check out below:-</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"5973\" class=\"wp-image-359496\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2021/03/Infographic-Final-Design.png\" alt=\"boost eCommerce sales\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2021/03/Infographic-Final-Design.png 1200w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2021/03/Infographic-Final-Design-60x300.png 60w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2021/03/Infographic-Final-Design-206x1024.png 206w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2021/03/Infographic-Final-Design-768x3823.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2021/03/Infographic-Final-Design-9x45.png 9w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2021/03/Infographic-Final-Design-300x1493.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons aligncenter\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-vivid-cyan-blue-background-color has-background\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Subscribe to our Newsletter</strong>!</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>I have Done All These, Now What?</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If you have done all the above already then you must also know how important it is to change sales techniques after a certain period because needs and preferences of consumers change too. You must also know how important it is to give your customers a user friendly and fulfilling experience of your business in order to increase your sales.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Good News! With our popular <a href=\"https://wphive.com/plugins/dokan-lite\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">WordPress plugin Dokan</a>, you can be flexible with how you wish to customize your eCommerce store and business. A multi-vendor eCommerce marketplace, Dokan allows you to <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/298981/create-online-shop-with-dokan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">create your own online marketplace</a> and add unlimited vendors. You can execute all of the above methods easily to generate more online sales, and you can also earn a commission from other vendors who work in your marketplace.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"559\" class=\"wp-image-348235\" src=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/08/60K-Active-Marketplaces-1024x559.png\" alt=\"dokan active installation\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/08/60K-Active-Marketplaces-1024x559.png 1024w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/08/60K-Active-Marketplaces-300x164.png 300w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/08/60K-Active-Marketplaces-768x420.png 768w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/08/60K-Active-Marketplaces-1536x839.png 1536w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/08/60K-Active-Marketplaces-45x25.png 45w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/08/60K-Active-Marketplaces-112x61.png 112w, https://cdn.wedevs.com/uploads/2020/08/60K-Active-Marketplaces.png 1622w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>For vendors, Dokan is the perfect solution because you can self-manage your business, it offers the best-looking storefront which is intuitive, and guarantees a satisfactory customer experience with all its built-in on-demand features. It is based on WooCommerce which is the best eCommerce solution today and as a vendor, you get full functionality from the frontend. Dokan also comes with a PRO version.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons aligncenter\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-luminous-vivid-amber-to-luminous-vivid-orange-gradient-background has-background\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/dokan/?utm_campaign=eCommerce&utm_medium=cta&utm_source=blog&utm_content=7\"><strong><em>Click to</em></strong> <em style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Learn More About Dokan Pro</em></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87132/proven-ways-to-boost-ecommerce-sales/\">9 Proven Ways to Boost Your eCommerce Sales</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/account\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://wedevs.com/blog/87132/proven-ways-to-boost-ecommerce-sales/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}